text: Laura Beatriz Suárez Hernandez (born 13 December 1998) is a Cuban female volleyball player. She is a member of the Cuba women's national volleyball team. She was part of the Cuban national team at the 2017 FIVB U23 World Championship and 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship. == References == == Other websites == * PER W: Cuban middle blockers duo joins Universidad César Vallejo Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Cuban volleyball players
